dct_title_s: South America, west coast : sheet VI, Chile : Tucapel Point to Point Lora
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and soundings. "Published according to Act of Parliament ... Augst. 24th. 1840. Corrections Feb. 1863." In lower right corner:1286. Inset: Coronel & Lota bays / by Captain Mallet of the Imperial French Navy, 1861. Includes 3 coastal profiles. "Soundings in fathoms." Historic Maps copy has ms. annotations.
dct_publisher_sm: [London] : Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ... ; Sold by J. D. Potter, agent for the Admiralty Charts ... , 1863.
